<p>
<note n="0176001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0176001">Paṭisaṅkhāra（修復）。</note>
<note n="0176001-1" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0176001-1">Mahāruci（大滿足）。</note>
<note n="0177002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0177002">Ruci（滿足）。</note>
<note n="0177003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0177003">Uparuci（近滿足）。</note>
<note n="0177001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0177001">讀為 Paramakāruññapatto（異本）。</note>
<note n="0178002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0178002">odana（乳麋）。</note>
<note n="0178001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0178001">Bandhumā 正寫為 Bandhumatī（親惠城）。</note>
<note n="0178002-1" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0178002-1">Vajirasama（金剛似）。</note>
<note n="0179001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0179001">Devagandha（天香）。</note>
<note n="0180001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0180001">波吒釐（Pāṭalī）樹為毘婆尸佛之菩提樹。</note>
<note n="0180002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0180002">Samantapāsādika（一切處愉悅）。</note>
<note n="0182001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0182001">讀為 sayane' bhivassanti（暹羅本）。</note>
<note n="0182002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0182002">讀為 Thitāsanthāraka（堅固蓆）（暹羅本）。</note>
<note n="0183001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0183001">Sucintita（善考）。</note>
<note n="0184001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0184001">Mahānigghosa（大響）。</note>
<note n="0184001-1" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0184001-1">此前之 Sucintita 略去。</note>
<note n="0184002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0184002">Kammāra（鐵工）Sūcidāyaka 嘗為鐵工匠，故作斯言。</note>
<note n="0185003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0185003">Dhammaka（法）。指 Buddhūpaṭṭhāka 長老。</note>
</p>
